<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.2">
<l>kaṉṉinaṉ māmatiḷ cūḻtaru pūmpoḻil kāvirit teṉṉa raṅkam</l>
<l>maṉṉiya cīrmatu cūtaṉā kēcavā pāviyēṉ vāḻvu kantu</l>
<l>uṉṉai yiḷaṅkaṉṟu mēykkac ciṟukālē yūṭṭi yoruppa ṭuttēṉ</l>
<l>eṉṉiṉ maṉamvali yāḷoru peṇillai yeṉkuṭṭa ṉēmut tamtā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Madhusūdana of enduring excellence</l>
<l rend="indent">in Southern Araṅkam on [the banks of]</l>
<l>The Kāveri with flower groves surrounded by fresh,</l>
<l rend="indent">beautiful, big natural walls! Kesavā!</l>
<l>Sinful me, desiring a happy life, I agreed to feed you at dawn</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [you could] graze the young calves.</l>
<l>There is no other woman as hard of heart than me.</l>
<l rend="indent">My boy! Give [me] a kiss!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
